# Transpersonal NPC Behavior Tree
# Consciousness-driven AI behavior for transpersonal NPCs

Root: Selector
├── Sequence: Emergency Response
│   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (PlayerThreatLevel > 0.8)
│   ├── Task: BTTask_ReactToThreat
│   └── Task: BTTask_SeekSafety
│
├── Sequence: Transformation State
│   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (bIsTransforming == true)
│   ├── Task: BTTask_PlayTransformationAnimation
│   ├── Wait: 2.0s
│   └── Task: BTTask_CompleteTransformation
│
├── Sequence: Player Interaction
│   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (PlayerInRange == true)
│   ├── Service: BTS_UpdatePlayerConsciousness
│   ├── Selector: Interaction Type
│   │   ├── Sequence: High Consciousness Interaction
│   │   │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (PlayerConsciousness > 0.7)
│   │   │   ├── Task: BTTask_OfferWisdom
│   │   │   └── Task: BTTask_TriggerTransformation
│   │   │
│   │   ├── Sequence: Medium Consciousness Interaction
│   │   │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (PlayerConsciousness > 0.4)
│   │   │   ├── Task: BTTask_EngageDialogue
│   │   │   └── Task: BTTask_ProvideGuidance
│   │   │
│   │   └── Sequence: Low Consciousness Interaction
│   │       ├── Task: BTTask_ChallengePlayer
│   │       └── Task: BTTask_RevealShadow
│   │
│   └── Task: BTTask_UpdateEmotionalResonance
│
├── Sequence: Consciousness Evolution
│   ├── Decorator: Cooldown (30.0s)
│   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (ConsciousnessLevel > EvolutionThreshold)
│   ├── Task: BTTask_EvolveConsciousness
│   └── Task: BTTask_UpdateBehaviorState
│
├── Sequence: Archetype Behavior
│   ├── Service: BTS_UpdateArchetypeBehavior
│   ├── Selector: Archetype Actions
│   │   ├── Sequence: Shadow Self
│   │   │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Archetype == ShadowSelf)
│   │   │   ├── Task: BTTask_LurkInShadows
│   │   │   └── Task: BTTask_EmergePeriodically
│   │   │
│   │   ├── Sequence: Wise Guide
│   │   │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Archetype == WiseGuide)
│   │   │   ├── Task: BTTask_Meditate
│   │   │   └── Task: BTTask_OfferBlessings
│   │   │
│   │   ├── Sequence: Inner Child
│   │   │   ├── Decorator: Blackboard (Archetype == InnerChild)
│   │   │   ├── Task: BTTask_PlayfulMovement
│   │   │   └── Task: BTTask_ExpressWonder
│   │   │
│   │   └── Task: BTTask_DefaultArchetypeBehavior
│   │
│   └── Task: BTTask_UpdateEmotionalState
│
└── Sequence: Default Behavior
    ├── Task: BTTask_Wander
    ├── Wait: Random(2.0, 5.0)
    └── Task: BTTask_IdleAnimation

Blackboard Keys:
- PlayerInRange (bool)
- PlayerConsciousness (float)
- PlayerThreatLevel (float)
- bIsTransforming (bool)
- ConsciousnessLevel (float)
- EmotionalState (float)
- Archetype (enum)
- EvolutionThreshold (float)
- LastInteractionTime (float)